WEBVTT

00:01.376 --> 00:05.214
<i>Full lockdown, now. No one gets in or out.</i>

00:05.214 --> 00:06.507
Hello, everyone.

00:06.507 --> 00:10.427
I am so sorry
for this temporary disruption.

00:10.427 --> 00:12.804
<i>The people behind this
will be apprehended.</i>

00:12.804 --> 00:14.473
Where's the fucking exit?

00:16.558 --> 00:19.937
