that your loved ones are in no danger.

00:19.937 --> 00:21.188
Thank you for your patience.

00:24.608 --> 00:27.694
Get the Bautistas taken somewhere private
right away. You understand?

00:27.694 --> 00:28.779
Do it. Go.

00:38.539 --> 00:40.874
Here you go, sir.
And take a deep breath of this.

00:42.251 --> 00:43.252
What the fuck's going on?

00:43.252 --> 00:45.754
