all over the fucking screen.

00:46.338 --> 00:48.131
<i>The investors are shitting their pants.</i>

00:48.131 --> 00:49.925
<i>We're covering every floor.</i>

00:51.927 --> 00:54.304
Get to the A/V room
and pull the fucking plug.

01:02.145 --> 01:03.814
